ces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T07:06:15.000Z","msg":"Btw <br />\n<br />\n連登仔好多都係中途政治友<br />\n<br />\n聽埋聽埋人哋鳩噏就當真<br />\n<br />\n大撚把泛民KOL由當日到今日都仲係話佢因為嗰件事肯定係鬼，講到共產黨派佢出嚟參選<br />\n<br />\n但係偏偏呢啲網台就係最多人聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n姚松嚴當日仲批評馮檢基叫晒記者公開影自己入廉政公署舉報係冇可能做到，肯定係投左共先做到，結果俾人搵返民主黨以前做過晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知隔左一個月到，班泛民竟然同馮檢基一樣，叫晒記者公開地走入廉政公署落案舉報人，真係人唔笑狗都吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T07:14:53.000Z","msg":"所以連登仔咪開返啲全世界入黎我哋就黎輸熱門無人講行動post無人推，點解？因為有資源的人唔做野，想做野的人無資源。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5a480819de24472493a46e8df55be3aeb970dcb","tid":1925102,"uid":49456,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T07:15:44.000Z","msg":"主流民意唔支持打交<br />\n抗爭無用<br />\n等埋g20 / 美國制裁 / 區選先<br />\n勇武抖抖，和班非進場<br />\n火魔裝修係黑警假扮<br />\n武力抗爭令美國人唔支持（打完立即過左人權法）<br />\n要支持中國人令佢地變成手足<br />\n支持加泰會激嬲美國（過左人權法）<br />\n所羅門提哂水 （毫無主見）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有叫人唔好唱願榮光，唔好嗌光復香港，時代革命<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢有講錯咩 你班友次次都錯判形勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b1c0b33f4efa9cca55aa15c649d49b9db102bf5","tid":1925102,"uid":137569,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5dec17aa91a9e9a0a4155